SUMMARY:Art Opening at Mayacamas Home
DESCRIPTION:Meet the Tim Weldon\, San Francisco mixed media artist as he exhibits recent works inspired by his studio environs in New Mexico. The paintings are fun\, evocative\, and wild. \nMayacamas Home is proud to present the works at this experiential gallery event. \nTour to the live music of flamenco guitarist El Oso.
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/art-opening-at-mayacamas-home/
