UID:10018379-1775593800-1775593800@golocal.coop
SUMMARY:Cass McCombs w/ Hand Habits at The Mystic Theatre
DESCRIPTION:Cass McCombs: \nOver the past twenty plus years\, Cass McCombs has journeyed a singular path as an \nuncompromising song-carver\, guitarist and singer. \nAlong with the finest squadron of collaborators and bandmates\, his music travels gracefully over \nseemingly contradictory terrain\, from infectious guitar riffage to intensely personal lyricism. \nIn 2024\, 4AD reissued his first three groundbreaking albums. In September\, Domino Records \nreleased a lost album from the same period\, Seed Cake On Leap Year. \nCass lives in New York City and is currently working on new recordings. \nHAND HABITS: \nFor artists who have built a creative practice centered around vulnerability\, what could possibly feel\nmore exposing? For Meg Duffy\, the multi-instrumentalist and songwriter known as Hand Habits\, it turns\nout there are things even more daunting than excavating unhappiness or grappling with personal identity.\n“For this record I had set out to write less as a way to process grief\, dredge up trauma\, or consider\nheartache\, and more as a way to tap into something that was surprisingly more challenging — to allow\nmyself to feel into in the given moment-the decision I made to no longer shape shift when it came to the\nperson I become in the face of love\,” explains Duffy.
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/cass-mccombs-w-hand-habits-at-the-mystic-theatre/
LOCATION:Mystic Theatre & Music Hall\, 23 Petaluma Blvd N\, Petaluma\, CA
CATEGORIES:Music
GEO:38.2334;-122.64
X-APPLE-STRUCTURED-LOCATION;VALUE=URI;X-ADDRESS=Mystic Theatre & Music Hall 23 Petaluma Blvd N Petaluma CA;X-APPLE-RADIUS=500;X-TITLE=23 Petaluma Blvd N:geo:-122.64,38.2334
END:VEVENT
