SUMMARY:Live Music Happy Hour - Pickin' Peaches!
DESCRIPTION:Downtown Santa Rosa ‘Golden Hour’ 4-7p | Live music 5-7 p | $6 beers & $2 off wine |Tuesday-Saturday!\nFor people who like to party…but want to be home at a reasonable hour…Pickin’ Peaches – Every Wednesday!\nAlong with their friends\, The Peaches play your favorite hits with a ukulele spin and wonderful harmonies.\n21+ Happy Hour Pricing 4-6pm All beers – $6 + $2 off wine & SABE cocktails. Live Music 5-7pm 2 drink minimum\, please.\nFree popcorn!\nCheck out www.BarrelProofLounge.com for all sorts of good times ahead!
