SUMMARY:Peacetown continues at HopMonk with Jenerator
DESCRIPTION:Jenerator is a collective of long-time friends and collaborators\, curated by Jen Rund. \nEach musician brings their own unique sound to Jenerator’s music\, giving a rich variety of expression to Jenerator’s catalogue of original tunes and covered favorites. Jen\, Mojo\, and Anna will be jammin’ for your dancing pleasure. Special guests? Hmmmm….. \nBorn and raised in northern California\, Jen Rund began her love affair with music at an early age. She played many instruments – cello\, clarinet\, piano\, guitar – before discovering the electric bass at 15. She went on to perform and record in a wide variety of genres\, including: rock\, pop\, folk\, Latin\, jazz\, R&B\, funk\, and blues\, in venues ranging from clubs to festivals. Jen has also enjoyed playing in ensembles for musical theater.
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/peacetown-continues-at-hopmonk-with-jenerator/
LOCATION:HopMonk Tavern – Sebastopol\, 230 Petaluma Ave\, Sebastopol\, CA
CATEGORIES:Music
GEO:38.4012;-122.823
