SUMMARY:West Side Stories Petaluma
DESCRIPTION:It’s the longest running StorySlam in Northern California! Everyday people have stories to tell and we have a stage to tell them on The Polly Klaas Community Theater located at 417 Western in Petaluma. You can (but are not required to) drop your name in the hat to tell a 5 Minute\, True Story\, Based on the theme of the night. You should get tickets in advance (we do tend to sell-out) at davepokornypresents.com
