SUMMARY:Stevie Cornell at Cafe Frida
DESCRIPTION:Award winning singer / songwriter \n  \nEclectic is the only way to describe Stevie’s music. And catchy! Over a long musical arc from 70s punk rock through early americana\, jazz\, film music\, electronica\, retro country western\, rockabilly he has always been restlessly devouring styles\, turning them inside out to see what makes them tick.
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/stevie-cornell-at-cafe-frida-4/
LOCATION:Cafe Frida Gallery\, 300 South A Street #4\, Santa Rosa\, CA
