SUMMARY:Thursday Sunset Paddle & Party at The Floathouse Petaluma
DESCRIPTION:Ease into the evening with a relaxed paddle on the Petaluma River\, followed by dockside snacks and community time at The Floathouse Petaluma\, right downtown in the central turning basin. No fuss\, no stress\, just community on the water with the sunset accompanying us. \nOnce a month from April through September\, paddlers gather for a 5:30 pm launch and head out together onto the calm tidal waters of the Petaluma River\, right in the heart of downtown. As the seasons shift\, the length of the paddle changes with the daylight—stretching into Sonoma County’s long summer evenings and shortening again as fall approaches. \nThe group returns to the dock about 30 minutes before sunset\, when everyone gathers to enjoy simple snacks\, good conversation\, and views of the evening sky over the river. \nRent one of The Floathouse’s stable sit-on-top kayaks or stand-up paddleboards\, or bring your own board or small boat and join the fun. This easygoing after-work outing is a great way to get outside\, connect with the river\, and meet fellow paddlers. \n2026 Dates: April 9 • May 21 • June 11 • July 9 • August 20 • September 24 \nPricing:\n$35 – Kayak or SUP rental for the duration of the paddle\n$10 – Bring your own board or boat \nOpen to SUP-per Club members and the public. To join the Floathouse SUP-per Club ($150 for 11 outings\, no expiration)\, see our website.
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/thursday-sunset-paddle-party-at-the-floathouse-petaluma-2/
LOCATION:The Floathouse Petaluma\, 50 Water Street\, Petaluma\, CA
CATEGORIES:Kids and Family,Recreation
GEO:38.23441;-122.63978
X-APPLE-STRUCTURED-LOCATION;VALUE=URI;X-ADDRESS=The Floathouse Petaluma 50 Water Street Petaluma CA;X-APPLE-RADIUS=500;X-TITLE=50 Water Street:geo:-122.63978,38.23441
END:VEVENT
