SUMMARY:Sebastian Saint James w/ Anna Jae Band & Diana Dreams at HopMonk Sebastopol
DESCRIPTION:CASA CENI PRESENTS \nSebastian Saint James feat: Mingo Lewis Jr. and Faith + Anna Jae Band + Diana Dreams \n  \nABOUT: \nSEBASTIAN SAINT JAMES \nSebastian Saint James\, Mingo Lewis Jr.\, and Faith come together in a collaborative project built around original songs performed through live looping\, percussion\, and layered vocals that grow in real time on stage. \nBlending indie blues\, funk\, soul\, and elements of lofi hip hop\, the trio builds each piece from the ground up with looping guitars\, deep rhythmic grooves\, and rich vocal harmonies. \nEach performance unfolds organically as the music is created live in the moment\, turning original ideas into hypnotic\, groove driven soundscapes. \nANNA JAE BAND \nAnna Jae is a Northern California singer-songwriter blending folk\, rock\, and 60s–70s soul into a sound that feels both nostalgic and deeply personal. With honey-warm vocals and storytelling lyrics\, she weaves originals alongside reimagined classics from Dylan to Janis. Whether solo or backed by her band\, Anna Jae brings heart\, grit\, and a little flower-child fire to every stage. \nDIANA DREAMS \nDark Magical Girl Music \nClassically-trained singer-songwriter Diana Dreams will share her unique blend of folk music\, pop/rock\, and classical ‘high drama’ music. \n 
URL:https://golocal.coop/event/sebastian-saint-james-w-anna-jae-band-diana-dreams-at-hopmonk-sebastopol/
LOCATION:HopMonk Tavern – Sebastopol\, 230 Petaluma Ave\, Sebastopol\, CA
CATEGORIES:Music
